# 🚀 ThriveX AI Mentor

ThriveX is your personal AI-powered growth companion. It listens to your voice, understands your emotions, and delivers real-time motivational advice through GPT-4 Turbo.

---

## 🎯 Features

- 🎙️ Voice-based interaction
- 🧠 Emotion detection (AI-enhanced or mocked for now)
- 💬 Motivational coaching with OpenAI GPT-4
- ☁️ Cloud-hosted via Streamlit
- 🔐 Secure API key management via `.streamlit/secrets.toml`

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Python + Streamlit
- OpenAI GPT-4 Turbo
- Whisper API (or local mic for devs)
- TensorFlow (optional for future emotion modeling)

---

## 🚀 Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Thrivex1123/ThriveX-AI-Mentor
cd ThriveX-AI-Mentor
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py

